title: Weekly Review with Clay and Buck H2 - May 7 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review with Clay and Buck H2 - May 7 2022
description:
Trump endorsement put JD Vance over the top in Ohio. Audience weighs in on abortion impact on the election. Editor-in-Chief of the National Pulse, Raheem Kassam joins Clay and Buck to give us the lowdown on Biden's Ministry of Truth czar, Nina Jankowicz (Soviet Mary Poppins) and new reporting on the "Birds Aren't Real" parody movement. Don't miss the C&B Mother's Day show this Friday. Leave a question for Clay and Buck's moms now on a dedicated line: 212-445-3969. We'll air the best ones on Friday! Randi Weingarten admits what we've been saying about covid and kids is true. Dr. Deborah Birx claims kids are in danger from covid.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
